{"tid":1444411,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實每次手足人數比狗隻多幾倍，如果最少4位手足夠唔夠砌一隻狗？","createTime":"2019-08-11T12:23:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:09:19.000Z","uid":153318,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"76b7009a59479677cf1e4ec54476ffd047482e6a","tid":1444411,"uid":153318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:23:18.000Z","msg":"頭先睇新聞尖沙咀有好幾位被制服，但被制服前都有位手足打到隻狗訓低，之後就走左，另一位手足咁就被制服<br />\n<br />\n4位手足打一隻狗應該夠打，起碼打到full gear狗隻起身都攤下攤下，相反手足裝備總比狗隻輕，容易走得快"},{"pid":"40df7301b19e4768988380ab5c9b21ba17dc7f5f","tid":1444411,"uid":173286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:28:41.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"0647d658df8d714b279db23b746933761d027096","tid":1444411,"uid":52939,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:31:30.000Z","msg":"佢有槍有煙有坦克咼"},{"pid":"e9c551cdb80ac743323af0c29f7252c9f282cec8","tid":1444411,"uid":25424,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:35:00.000Z","msg":"4打1一定贏<br />\n不過唔出手打俾100個你對一個警察都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00dfc2e5954a328f87c3fd7124c92e3f29d44f63","tid":1444411,"uid":153318,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e9c551cdb80ac743323af0c29f7252c9f282cec8","tid":1444411,"uid":25424,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:35:00.000Z","msg":"4打1一定贏<br />\n不過唔出手打俾100個你對一個警察都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:39:30.000Z","msg":"而家呢個地步，打同唔打都被狗捉，死人都打啦！但只怕手足互不相識，唔知有冇呢種密契幫手打，做到打完一個不能少全身而退"},{"pid":"b021be7d7e5611cce7a2c6aa66e47087a007e26c","tid":1444411,"uid":33875,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:41:14.000Z","msg":"肯食彈同肯還拖係兩種境界，尤其還拖要多人組隊，但而家根本唔知邊個係人係鬼"},{"pid":"f07f0813a6ff79f46c59d668eb64198de025aa87","tid":1444411,"uid":280547,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b021be7d7e5611cce7a2c6aa66e47087a007e26c","tid":1444411,"uid":33875,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:41:14.000Z","msg":"肯食彈同肯還拖係兩種境界，尤其還拖要多人組隊，但而家根本唔知邊個係人係鬼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:42:26.000Z","msg":"師兄全中"},{"pid":"524ceecf17b54e7210c9ecc41b8a25cb50e7fab3","tid":1444411,"uid":153318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:50:30.000Z","msg":"但如果有手足一個唔好彩被狗㩒地，其他手足唔使多，10位8位去幫拖救人兼打另外增援的狗。當然一定要量力而為<br />\n<br />\n大前提係唔好主動撩狗打"},{"pid":"4ed8258ac8d74e54dace62f140f82c48a49c37fc","tid":1444411,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:51:00.000Z","msg":"一定夠"},{"pid":"74983f5edf63cc3f717bd52792eee212c1324232","tid":1444411,"uid":118240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00dfc2e5954a328f87c3fd7124c92e3f29d44f63","tid":1444411,"uid":153318,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e9c551cdb80ac743323af0c29f7252c9f282cec8","tid":1444411,"uid":25424,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:35:00.000Z","msg":"4打1一定贏<br />\n不過唔出手打俾100個你對一個警察都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:39:30.000Z","msg":"而家呢個地步，打同唔打都被狗捉，死人都打啦！但只怕手足互不相識，唔知有冇呢種密契幫手打，做到打完一個不能少全身而退"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:51:04.000Z","msg":"難<br />\n我假設有一個警察係你面前（仲要唔知點解得一個）<br />\n以示威時候既情況<br />\n我當你地同佢有50-100m距離<br />\n你地衝埋去佢一定夠時間拎起支槍<br />\n你哋四個一定至少會死一個"},{"pid":"5b42d68dae5a0c08a2645a4f018c42cfc510d950","tid":1444411,"uid":21920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:51:30.000Z","msg":"要前線人士自己組左隊先得"},{"pid":"22e66e5ea9aaa6ab0ad8a66a47bb71903770b77a","tid":1444411,"uid":287048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:52:53.000Z","msg":"其實速龍裝備只係一隻手揸棍，一隻手空<br />\n比北角福建佬/元朗白衣人容易對付，前線5/8見到福建佬都唔淆啦，<br />\n咁點解見到速龍唔可以保持密度，甚至幾十人一齊正面衝過去?<br />\n好似沙田個次咁，只要有幾個唔怕死對速龍正面打，後面其他人都會湧上前跟住打。<br />\n<br />\n同埋黑警出速龍時，就唔會出我哋最驚嘅橡膠彈/實彈，所以夠膽圍揪，人多就一定贏。"},{"pid":"21c962c151d8ae29e9fe3bb83c82aa164eb55400","tid":1444411,"uid":277540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:52:56.000Z","msg":"4-5 個圍一個都唔夠薑  打L 返佢轉頭"},{"pid":"18aad3d0a73dedee1beaac6c99e375f04c46640d","tid":1444411,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:54:03.000Z","msg":"打贏幾隻但要被拉"},{"pid":"5ad77a063bc87b7360ea62cfd74d582b4c0e3c4c","tid":1444411,"uid":153318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18aad3d0a73dedee1beaac6c99e375f04c46640d","tid":1444411,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:54:03.000Z","msg":"打贏幾隻但要被拉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:42:01.000Z","msg":"唔打又被拉，打又被打<br />\n女傷者中布袋彈永久失明<br />\n太古站無差別地掃射<br />\n<br />\n仲忍！？"},{"pid":"80053ac036bb88918c5bd2e8bbef62be9b5b8b77","tid":1444411,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ad77a063bc87b7360ea62cfd74d582b4c0e3c4c","tid":1444411,"uid":153318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18aad3d0a73dedee1beaac6c99e375f04c46640d","tid":1444411,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:54:03.000Z","msg":"打贏幾隻但要被拉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:42:01.000Z","msg":"唔打又被拉，打又被打<br />\n女傷者中布袋彈永久失明<br />\n太古站無差別地掃射<br />\n<br />\n仲忍！？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:09:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}